==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tup
<hw>Tup</hw> <pr>(t⟦ucr⟧p)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[Probably
akin to <ets>top</ets> summit, head.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To butt, as
a ram does.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To cover; -- said of a ram.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tup</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
